{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1783781110592", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "tool_use", "id": "chatcmpl-tool-bebf14cbf30df856", "name": "Agent", "input": {"description": "Fetch arXiv paper PDF", "prompt": "I need you to download and read the arXiv paper at https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.07985v1 (arXiv ID: 2607.07985). The paper title is \"A Reliability Assessment of LALM Audio Judges for Full-Duplex Voice Agents\".\n\nTry to download the PDF and extract its text. Use:\n1. First try: wget or curl to download the PDF from https://arxiv.org/pdf/2607.07985v1\n2. Then use pdftotext or python to extract text\n3. If PDF extraction fails, try the arXiv API or HTML version\n\nReturn the FULL text content of the paper - all sections, tables, figures descriptions, appendix, references. I need the complete paper text to do a thorough review. If you can only get the abstract, say so explicitly.\n\nDo NOT modify any files in any git repository. Just download and extract text, then return it to me.", "subagent_type": "general-purpose"}}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "2323bd30-3aaf-46fe-8f3f-f54d2b380792", "uuid": "32f709a7-7a14-42e0-9b8d-4ed21b4b4212"}
